title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync
description: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync
OB: When using the JarExporter tool, the exported jar file includes itself, causing an out of sync issue.
EB: The exported jar file should not include itself to prevent the out of sync issue.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Use the JarExporter tool to export a jar file. 
2. Inspect the exported jar file and verify that it includes itself. 
3. Notice the out of sync behavior that occurs as a result.
